349
00:19:02,987 --> 00:19:05,087
Polisi melakukan kesalahan tentang itu, bukan?

350
00:19:05,087 --> 00:19:06,887
Apa maksudmu darah di peti mati itu

351
00:19:06,887 --> 00:19:10,887
