367
00:21:18,887 --> 00:21:21,987
Ya. Tampaknya dia berbohong pada kepala pelayan

368
00:21:21,987 --> 00:21:24,487
yang dia pikir berkhianat.

369
00:21:24,487 --> 00:21:26,387
